const faqs = [
  {
    question: "What areas of Bellevue do you serve?",
    answer: "We serve all of Bellevue and surrounding areas including homes along Highway 70, Old Hickory Boulevard, Harpeth Valley, River Plantation, Poplar Creek Estates, Temple Hills, and throughout the greater Bellevue community. From starter homes to executive properties, we bring quality cleaning services to every Bellevue residence."
  },
  {
    question: "Do you service homes near the Harpeth River and in flood-prone areas?",
    answer: "Yes, we serve all Bellevue areas including those near the beautiful Harpeth River. We understand that homes in certain areas may have specific cleaning needs related to humidity or occasional water issues. We're experienced in thorough cleaning that addresses these unique considerations."
  },
  {
    question: "How do you handle Bellevue's variety of home styles and sizes?",
    answer: "Bellevue features tremendous variety, from cozy 1,500 square foot homes to spacious 4,000+ square foot properties. We customize our service to match your home's size and needs. Our pricing scales appropriately so you're paying for your actual home, not a one-size-fits-all approach."
  },
  {
    question: "Can you accommodate busy commuter schedules?",
    answer: "Absolutely! Many Bellevue residents commute to downtown Nashville or other employment centers. We offer flexible scheduling and can clean while you're at work. Most clients provide garage codes or smart lock access so they can return home to a clean house without any scheduling hassles."
